

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <!-- 引用google字體 -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!--  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <!-- 引用fontawesome icon -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/da3a6ce48e.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/jquery.js"></script>
    <title>ShyKid</title>
</head>

<body>
    
    @*<partial name="_Notification" />*@
    <!-- 頭部圖片顯示 -->
    <main>
        <section class="backImage">
            <div class="filter"></div>
            <h3>可以讓你分享領養資訊，想領養或了解狗、想曬自家毛小孩
                <br>
                一個讓大家討論的地方
            </h3>
            <button class="start"><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Member" asp-action="Singup" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">歡迎加入</a></button>
        </section>
    </main>

    <div class="art-title">
        <h4>
            前往使用
        </h4>
    </div>

    <!-- 中間圖檔顯示 -->
    <div class="main-item">
        <div class="shell">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="images">
                    <img src="/img/dog01.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2><a asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">張貼領養</a></h2>
                    <p>分享需要新主人的狗狗資訊、從路邊救援、自家新出生小狗等等</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <div class="images">
                    <img src="/img/dog02.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Adoption">我想領養</a></h2>
                    <p>想多一個動物陪伴、已經了解身為主人的義務與責任，並可以負責照顧</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <div class="images">
                    <img src="/img/dog03.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h2><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Forum">討論曬狗</a></h2>
                    <p>
                        我想曬自家毛小孩，不論是照片、還是心得，可以一起討論
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
</body>

</html>